- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper evaluates the performance of different models on tasks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the ability of models to understand and represent language. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper evaluates models on a task related to word-sense discrimination. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper may involve the use of neural networks for representation learning.
